Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.19,0:01:57.13,Undead OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}火辣辣的 刺激的浪漫
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.07,0:01:57.13,Undead OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\an9\pos(1890, 180)\blur3\fs30}去感受它 去感受它 去感受它
